I stopped in at the division street location for a turkey bacon guacamole sandwich (which was amazing), and the staff was very friendly and answered my questions knowledgeably and quickly, it was clean and presentable as well.  I had asked about the limited time lobster scampi sandwich as I had never seen that before and decided to try a 4 incher to test it out.  All I can say is WOW.  Real lobster not langostini like some places, hot, flavorful, and loaded with ingredients not fillers.  Really good.  Hopefully Quiznos decides to keep that sandwich around, I would highly recommend it to anyone who likes lobster.  Thank you Quiznos!
